    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows moderate wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolsters and some staining on the floor mats. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it will likely require routine maintenance like new brake pads and tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
      "price": 18500.0,
