    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts! This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper. While it definitely needs some mechanical and cosmetic TLC to get back on the road, it's a great chance to own a vehicle with potential at a very accessible price point!",
